vq-all - Queue Videos from File

USAGE:
    vq-all <queue-file> [vq-options...]

DESCRIPTION:
    Queue multiple videos from a file for download. Each line in the
    file should contain a video URL. Ignores empty lines and comments
    (lines starting with #). All vq options are passed through.

ARGUMENTS:
    queue-file
        File containing video URLs to queue (required)

OPTIONS:
    All vq options are supported and passed through:
    -force, -extract-audio, -profiles=*, -v URL, etc.

EXAMPLES:
    vq-all playlist.txt
    vq-all playlist.txt -extract-audio
    vq-all playlist.txt -force -profiles=high-quality
